# RABS eval run configuration

compiler: g++ (MinGW-w64) -O2 -std=c++17
compiler_version: 13.1.0
repetitions_per_combo: 30
main_grid: 5 scenarios x 4 budget levels x 4 baseline/production policies + RABS = 5 policies
total_main_runs: 3000
ablation_grid: 5 scenarios x 4 budget levels x {RABS, RABS_NoRisk}
total_ablation_runs: 1200
risk_threshold: 0.4
max_file_bytes_skip_threshold: 1073741824 (1 GB, matches production HungerCfg::kMaxFileBytes)
note: synthetic population model, no real files created/deleted; deletion outcomes are a seeded
      Bernoulli failure model (see deletionFailureProb in rabs_eval.cpp).

