CPU: 11th Gen Intel(R) Core(TM) i5-11400H @ 2.70GHz
RAM: 31.8 GB
Disk: Hitachi HTS545032B9A300 (HDD)
OS: Microsoft Windows 11 Pro 10.0.26200 (Build 26200)
Qt SDK installed: 6.11.1 (harness itself does not link Qt; Qt version listed for parity with
                   the production TrashPet AI app, built with the same MinGW 13.1.0 toolchain)
Compiler: MinGW-w64 g++ 13.1.0, -O2 -std=c++17
Repetitions actually run: 30 per (scenario, budget_level) combo
Total planning runs executed: 3000 (main grid) + 1200 (ablation grid) = 4200
